{"tid":1876371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王祖藍聯合93明星向武漢捐贈20救護車","createTime":"2020-02-12T10:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T11:27:08.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"331d95e892e7762a4596339b572c3f9d409024c2","tid":1876371,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"醫護人員日以繼夜在全國各地對抗新冠肺炎疫情，醫療裝備出現短缺，但不少醫護人員仍堅守崗位，拼命為民服務。因此明星們紛紛通過各種渠道和人脈，在全世界各地購買醫療防護物資。<br />\n<br />\n近日93位愛心明星，包括王祖藍李亞男夫婦、黃曉明楊穎夫婦、張柏芝、李冰冰、秦嵐、陳偉霆、魏大勛、姚晨、胡彥斌、張雨綺等，聯合中華思源工程扶貧基金會（以下簡稱：思源工程）再向雷神山醫院、火神山醫院交付14輛負壓救護車，累計交付20輛（每家各10輛）並投入使用，助力醫院開展新冠肺炎患者救治等工作。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：文匯報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAiX1U0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAiX1U0.jpg&h=8e59afe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd6ee96be4a372364cc3bb52681f9386f7250dbd","tid":1876371,"uid":81657,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"加快運送屍體火化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68274d4f6762bd0db1c5b96ff02409e0157041aa","tid":1876371,"uid":132189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"香港呢？"},{"pid":"5140ccc21dcb34b127620600fa64ed68660eb579","tid":1876371,"uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"唔上埋去救人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794bcf74d1c282d81dbe8417e6cf4d4ba056ddad","tid":1876371,"uid":27451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"香港就 豆零都唔損，正垃圾"},{"pid":"7f4690286b5fc1a951a446ad9539dd4d7542bfd9","tid":1876371,"uid":210922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"唔見你捐口罩比香港，你老味臭西"},{"pid":"baac8b713e84cf65bf7c78f7deead3c3051ad1aa","tid":1876371,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:59:38.000Z","m